			"condition": "!!jibo && jibo.isBirthday && jibo.age.days.value > 1",
			"prompt": "My power went on for the first time exactly ${jibo.age.supplemented} ago, <anim cat=\"emoji\" filter=\"cake, !hot-frame\" nonBlocking=\"true\" />which makes today my birthday. Happy Birthday Jibo, if I do say so myself.",
