			"condition": "!!jibo && jibo.isBirthday && jibo.age.days.value > 1",
			"prompt": "Funny you should <anim cat=\"emoji\" filter=\"cake, !hot-frame\" nonBlocking=\"true\" />ask, today's my birthday. I was first powered up ${jibo.age.supplemented} ago today. <break size='0.3'/> Seems like just yesterday.",
